{"tid":656708,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"醫生：未來數周對費Sir好重要！","createTime":"2018-05-07T12:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T16:45:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7182be2c840ebd74a84d2be70a11bd80cf069c28","tid":656708,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=smGWapF1gBtCZO2bCLKnjvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=42945c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】神經外科醫生表示，剛做腦出血手術的曼聯傳奇領隊費格遜，在未來數周的情況對日後康復十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n76歲的費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）上周六於家中跌倒後，因為腦出血入院，手術成功後仍然留在深切治療病房，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n英國《電訊報》就費Sir的情況諮詢了神經外科醫生夏連（Peter Hamlyn），後者表示：「以費Sir的情況，他要立即做手術因為醫生們認為腦中的血塊太大了，那時正在損壞腦部組織。這通常是個救命的手術，主要希望減少長遠的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n夏連續說：「手術後數天，關鍵在於病者的生命支持，但要過數星期才能預測他的康復進度。病者有機會完全回復之前的身體狀況，但要是在未來數月都沒有好轉，就很難可以百分百痊癒。」"},{"pid":"7e321cbb1af17a92e819104d1b807a59786ea2ce","tid":656708,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"尊重費蛇 但49000要繼續反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8efc66d36fd62cb21af1e9ca8f02788a5439a3d","tid":656708,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad2e28a97e8bafb7d8ce1097153ce6941203ab0","tid":656708,"uid":7940,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8efc66d36fd62cb21af1e9ca8f02788a5439a3d","tid":656708,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"長命D睇住獌狗降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72e0c101894fb784e6a3f548b12b40227f258ca","tid":656708,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q